{!<span class="tooltip-text" title="Rangers are a paramilitary group loosely under the command of the Gendarmerie, tasked with the protection of villages, towns and rural areas against insurgencies.">Rangers</span>!} Strength: [+ rb_strength_2 +] thousand

Rangers Militarization: [+ rb_militancy : militancy +]

